metadata.dc:description: A case of a nonseptated cystic hygroma with spontaneous resolution in utero is presented. The clinic, sonographic, and morphologic findings as well as the prognosis of septated and nonseptated cystic hygromas are discussed.
metadata.dc:title: Regresión espontánea de un higroma quístico.
[Spontaneous regression of a cystic hygroma].
metadata.dc:publisher: Revista chilena de obstetricia y ginecologia
